name: Populate
description: PopulateChunkEvent.Populate is fired when a chunk is populated with a terrain feature. This event is fired during terrain feature generation in ChunkProviderEnd.populate(int, int) , ChunkProviderOverworld.populate(int, int) , and ChunkProviderHell.populate(int, int) . type contains the enum value for the terrain feature being generated. This event is not Cancelable . This event has a result. HasResult This result determines if the chunk is populated with the terrain feature. This event is fired on the MinecraftForge.EVENT_BUS .
